VideoLAN (VLC) has a forum, where you can ask questions, get help or make suggestions for improvement.


If you have a question, you can probably find an answer on one of these pages:
* [[Common Problems]]
* [https://www.videolan.org/doc/ Documentation]
* Or see if the question has been answered before by [https://forum.videolan.org/search.php searching the forum]
Check these before posting a new question as it will save you time waiting for a response at the forum.


The forum is at '''https://forum.videolan.org'''

